data.title: Shintōhō Eiga
data.meta_description: Shintōhō Eiga  is a Japanese pink film production company and film distributor located in Tokyo, Japan which has been among the most influential studios in the pink film genre since its beginnings.
data.text:
For the mainstream film company which went bankrupt in 1961, see Shintoho

Shintōhō Eiga (新東宝映画, lit. Shintoho Pictures) is a Japanese pink film production company and film distributor located in Tokyo, Japan which has been among the most influential studios in the pink film genre since its beginnings.
